&lt;li&gt;Conduct economic and industry research to analyse business models and market trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the analysis of financial, operational, and macroeconomic information that helps value businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the creation of financial models and the development of key valuation parameters.&lt;/li&gt;
