&lt;li&gt;Assisting in analysis or preparation of valuations and the processing and use of big data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing the workload and tasks of the project team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing budgets and fee reports;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dealing with clients and lawyers and interfacing as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviewing documentation (e.g. drawings, specifications, reports, estimates, variations, correspondence and financial data) to develop robust appendices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
